Release Notes for Version 3.11.6
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.11.6 is the 7th release in
the Errata Tool 3.11 development period. It closes [6 bugs and RFEs][buglist].

This release's highlights include support for workflow that excludes TPS-RHNQA
and some safeguards against performance issues caused by fetching large
amounts of data in a single request.

